title: Let's Talk - Lead her to look... Part 5

media:group.media:title: Let's Talk - Lead her to look... Part 5
media:group.media:description: Dads, our series for dads of daughters continues this Wednesday with “Lead her to LOOK.” Your daughter is asking lots of questions—and hearing opinions from lots of voices—about life and relationships. How can you make sure your voice and your perspective are heard and are influential in her life? Tune in for some ideas from Drs. Ken & Michelle.
